data.text:
Mark is a member of B.O.S., an international group for hunters. He volunteers at the animal shelter in his free time.

In-game bio

Mark is a character in Coral Island and one of the 28 available marriage candidates. He lives in the Woodlands with Anne, Paul, and Zoe, their house is located right next to the Lake. He is only available after 5th Spring Year 1.

Personality[]

Mark is often cold when interacting with others. He shows a soft spot for animals, sometimes talking about how he wishes he could set them free from their pens, acknowledging that it isn't the smartest idea at the same time.

Relationships[]

Mark first meets the player in front of their house on Spring 5 informing them that the Cavern is now open, at the end of the interaction he remarks that the conversation was a waste of time.

Mark lives with Zoe (his niece), Anne (his sister), and Paul (his brother-in-law) near the Lake, and speaks highly of them.

He is shown to respect and trust Kira, but seems to keep his distance from other B.O.S. members.
